>\n冇咩其他可能可以真正改變現狀<br />\n靠選舉靠外國都係幻想下好啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T09:07:18.000Z","msg":"所以依家淨係嗌口號就爭取到？"},{"pid":"33259657a108ed460a481d24a200fba0c54600a3","tid":1896593,"uid":50588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f774eb3061bc4f96e6afd7369c50fcdea187cad2","tid":1896593,"uid":136227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"12c1c078d8b746acfd9b909f229455d35ffef340","tid":1896593,"uid":50588,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"794c4e483f84aaa27efc84235ef53a4def3783da","tid":1896593,"uid":136227,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T08:42:19.000Z","msg":"照你咁講<br />\n即係支共倒台前就咩都唔做唔試？<br />\n佛系抗爭？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T08:43:57.000Z","msg":"邊到有講咩都唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你心入邊得呢兩個選項？<br />\n咁唔失敗都幾難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T08:51:02.000Z","msg":"留意返係你話除左倒台之外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好自打嘴巴<br />\n<br />\n功能組別搶走建制既票<br />\n嘗試改變議會投票樣樣都過既問題先<br />\n起碼香港人有機會有say<br />\n雖然唔知結果<br />\n但唔試就一定唔得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T09:07:27.000Z","msg":"咁係你覺得係倒台入邊冇野做到姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多人只係淺黄 佢哋會滿足於呢啲'階段性勝利'<br />\n基本上呢個勢形成左之後 就冇可能再有機會倒支共<br />\n之後支共醒啲嘅話一樣可以繼續慢慢同化同驅逐香港人"},{"pid":"6fad53d8d27ae3e0e981f11be94ff9695ef1efff","tid":1896593,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislik